SPECIAL WIRE COMES INTO PLAY HERE
you will plug your female end of the 1 directional cut wire into the keyboard switch and then glue that dupoint casing to the pla wall
then route the stripped end through the cap pull tight and then seal with hot glue and then plug the stripped ends into your female wires
going 1 wire to gnd and 1 wire to d14 does not matter orientation.
Keyboard Switch (Button):
  Connect one terminal to GND (Row 1, Column A).
  Connect the other terminal to GPIO 14.
LED:
  Short Leg (GND): Connect to Row 17, Column I.
  Long Leg (Anode): Connect to GPIO 15.
